These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, egyptian, british, malaysian
1. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
2. the malaysian is between the italian and the egyptian##2
3. the malaysian is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | italian | malaysian | egyptian | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, pumpkin, nectarine, pineapple
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | pumpkin | asparagus | pineapple | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, superhero, animation, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
2. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching superhero movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | horror | animation | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, tennis, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
2. the person who's sport is tennis is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | rugby | ice-hockey | basketball | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
