2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | volleyball | golf | cycling | climbing |

