.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, indian, italian, american
1. the indian is on the far right##1
2. the indian is on the left or right of the american##3
3. the italian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian | pakistani | american | indian |

