.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, train, taxi
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | train | boat | taxi | quad-bike |

