1. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking milk##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | juice | milk | iced-tea |

