.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, potato, pomegranate, cucumber
1. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating orange is in an even position##4
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | pomegranate | cucumber | potato | orange |

